" />我up唔到相"},{"pid":"920379fc304a67707b3e35881affa8adcb00f1d7","tid":1542411,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"[律師建議］ 緊急 請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n831太子站當日有份俾人打嘅市民，請盡快聯絡律師做民事訴訟(personal injuries)，向法庭申請要地鐵攞CCTV。<br />\n<br />\n一定要快，如果過咗期限，地鐵話自動洗咗啲CCTV，到時就真係冇人知道太子發生過咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：其實唔止身體受傷，心靈受創都可以告。當日喺現場目擊事件，造成精神痛苦，都可以嘗試用 secondary victim （非直接受害人）去追討。最後告唔告得入唔係最重要，目的係令多啲人有權拎CCTV，還原真相⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 98190979<br />\n民陣 65499452<br />\n民權觀察 94632945<br />\n伍展邦律師行 26081400<br />\n<br />\n推呀！！唔想有人抄車，但更加唔想抄左車但冇人知！！黑警一定要還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究到底！啦<br />\n<br />\n想自保都有野幫到手!<br />\n如果想自保，請所有知情人士立即錄影一片短片(遮樣，但一定要仔細描述當時情況)，將你所知既細節送去各大媒體，並響9月5日中午12點前，以匿名方式送到各大媒體(報章、社交媒體)。當呢件事徹底曝光，響公眾既注視下，你地先會真正既安全<br />\n<br />\n知道你地可能有好多各方面擔心 但想知真相得一個方法 就係拎到cctv 唔想搞民氏訴訟 都幫手拍條片send去各大媒體啊<br />\n求下你地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盡力幫幫手<br />\n如果拎到 我地離革命成功 又遇進一大步ga啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9125d95d1e60059d1cc35e204fb8fa30dc255d19","tid":1542411,"uid":197379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"986345cab32c0e250ea58aa567a4ddeb53a24c21","tid":1542411,"uid":75668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UE0o2VK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUE0o2VK.png&h=e595db36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d1a2440d3a6783cb55dd6dcadef2253325d5714","tid":1542411,"uid":212904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:40:17.000Z","msg":"尋日朝太和站都有，但好多人返工行過都屌狗，到今朝冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b0dd678725013543a9f359b834aa4c4bb7f065","tid":1542411,"uid":210692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0157ba1075245200939dff094d38b58fa709b1e8","tid":1542411,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:29:15.000Z","msg":"行過石硤尾站非付款通道，好多有盾同棍嘅蛆，可能其他站都係。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱都經過<br />\n狗仲多過人<br />\n仲要陰陰濕濕企柱後面<br />\n差啲撞埋去"},{"pid":"27d875690c34fd444bd2d878baced725de2dde39","tid":1542411,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:41:44.000Z","msg":"做埋查飛狗嗰份幫手捉跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597fdbd926bf517484090de1c20ed734c7f0818e","tid":1542411,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4b0dd678725013543a9f359b834aa4c4bb7f065","tid":1542411,"uid":210692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0157ba1075245200939dff094d38b58fa709b1e8","tid":1542411,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:29:15.000Z","msg":"行過石硤尾站非付款通道，好多有盾同棍嘅蛆，可能其他站都係。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱都經過<br />\n狗仲多過人<br />\n仲要陰陰濕濕企柱後面<br />\n差啲撞埋去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:44:31.000Z","msg":"真係行過，眼尾見到成班蛆喺度，睇唔到其他出口有冇，應該想捉跳閘嘅手足"},{"pid":"e85f205f7c8e3f87256a71d299522fbf3704cdaf","tid":1542411,"uid":159557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"柯士甸咁耐都無出過事，我覺得班狗擺明做戲比班